# Bool Tool Documentation
This directory contains the source and configuration for the documentation site of this project. Documentation is written in Markdown (`.md`) and built with [Sphinx](https://www.sphinx-doc.org/) (and the [Furo](https://github.com/pradyunsg/furo) theme).

## Structure
```
documentation/
├── build/          # Generated output (gitignored)
├── config/         # Sphinx configuration
├── pages/          # Documentation content (.md files)
├── make.bat        # Build script for Windows
├── Makefile        # Build script for Linux/macOS
└── requirements.txt
```

## Requirements
- Sphinx
- Furo (theme)
- [`myst-parser`](https://myst-parser.readthedocs.io/en/latest/)

Install the documentation dependencies with `pip`:

```bash
pip install -r documentation/requirements.txt
```

## Building the docs
**Windows:**
```bat
documentation/make.bat html
```

**Linux/macOS** (requires [GNU Make](https://www.gnu.org/software/make/)):
```bash
documentation/make html
```

The built site will be added in `build/html`. Open `build/html/index.html` in a browser to preview the documentations website locally.
